com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport

Class ItemPlaceholder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.CoreItem
      • com.i2group.apollo.model.data.transport.ItemPlaceholder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityPlaceholder, LinkPlaceholder

    public abstract class ItemPlaceholder
extends CoreItem
    A generic representation for EntityPlaceholders and LinkPlaceholders that provides the features common to both.

    i2 Analyze returns placeholders instead of Items in situations where returning the full Item is not possible or not permitted. This can be the case due to security considerations, for example, or when the requested Item has been deleted, or purged, or merged into another Item.

    Since:
    1.0
